&gt; Could you please advise me who will be attending? 
We have not begun registration, but it appears that the core WCAG members (those who have been attending teleconference calls regularly) will be able to attend the WCAG meetings on Thursday and Friday (5 &amp;amp; 6 October). 
I'm not sure who from the Authoring Tool Working Group will join us on Friday afternoon. 
&gt; is there an agenda? 
There is not yet a detailed agenda, although the main point of the meetings is to discuss the next revision of WCAG. 
&gt; would it be helpful, if I was present? 
sure. 
&gt; with someone with learning difficulties? 
even better. 
&gt; to demonstrate problems regarding web accessibility? 
Sounds interesting! 
